{
    "manually_checked": false,
    "poem_title": "A Justa",
    "author": "Salvador Bermúdez de Castro",
    "poem_alt_title": "Cuando un tiempo cansado en su camino",
    "corpus": "disco2_1",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": "1",
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "1",
                    "line_text": "Cuando un tiempo cansado en su camino",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-++--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "2",
                    "line_text": "el ardiente Israelita vacilaba,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "3",
                    "line_text": "a consolar su espíritu llagaba,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "4",
                    "line_text": "vertiendo aromas, querubín divino.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Cuando un tiempo cansado en su camino\nel ardiente Israelita vacilaba,\na consolar su espíritu llagaba,\nvertiendo aromas, querubín divino."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "2",
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "5",
                    "line_text": "Y si luego en el aire cristalino",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "6",
                    "line_text": "sus alas desplegando se alejaba,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "7",
                    "line_text": "un rayo siempre de su faz guiaba",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "8",
                    "line_text": "al fatigado, errante peregrino.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Y si luego en el aire cristalino\nsus alas desplegando se alejaba,\nun rayo siempre de su faz guiaba\nal fatigado, errante peregrino."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "3",
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "9",
                    "line_text": "Así al mirar de la fortuna el ceño,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "10",
                    "line_text": "evoco un bien, oh Justa, en mi memoria,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+++-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "11",
                    "line_text": "que es de mis males celestial beleño.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Así al mirar de la fortuna el ceño,\nevoco un bien, oh Justa, en mi memoria,\nque es de mis males celestial beleño."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "4",
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "12",
                    "line_text": "Y en mis pesares, cándida, ilusoria,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "13",
                    "line_text": "tu hermosa imagen, cual divino ensueño,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "14",
                    "line_text": "el alma inunda con fulgor de gloria.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Y en mis pesares, cándida, ilusoria,\ntu hermosa imagen, cual divino ensueño,\nel alma inunda con fulgor de gloria."
        }
    ]
}